						<div class="postbody">In any case, you can probably skip much of your rendering code if the tab is not visible (Page Visibility API) and the mapper doesn't snoop on PPU reads (like MMC2 and MMC4, and to a lesser extent MMC3 and JY). Only the scanlines containing sprite 0 or containing at least 8 sprites have any effect that the rest of the system can see.</div>

